# Audapp Channels (Phase 21F) — compile-only separate-root multi-endpoint scaffold.
#
# Git policy (per Phase 21B/21F decision): commit ONLY Audapp-owned files.
# The Microsoft-derived ACX AudioCodec sample source is intentionally NOT
# committed (licensing / provenance), matching the audapp-input/audapp-multi
# scaffolds. Those files live on-disk only and are reproduced by copying from
# driver/scaffold/audapp-multi + applying the documented Phase 21F edits
# (Device.cpp channel-selection, RenderCircuit.cpp single-circuit helper,
# Public.h prototype).
#
# Tracked (Audapp-owned): shared/Channels.h,
# project/upstream-audiocodec/AudioChannels.inf, build-channels.ps1,
# Generate-Catalog-channels.ps1, Sign-Catalog-channels.ps1, and scaffold docs.

# --- Build artifacts / intermediates ---
Common/x64/
project/build/
project/out/
project/*.binlog
project/*.log
*.log
package/
**/x64/Debug/
**/x64/Release/

# --- Microsoft-derived ACX sample source (NOT committed) ---
Common/*.cpp
Common/*.h
Common/*.vcxproj
Common/*.vcxproj.*
inc/*.h
shared/Public.h
shared/Trace.h
project/upstream-audiocodec/Device.cpp
project/upstream-audiocodec/Driver.cpp
project/upstream-audiocodec/DriverSettings.h
project/upstream-audiocodec/Resources.rc
project/upstream-audiocodec/ReadMe.txt
project/upstream-audiocodec/AudioCodec.sln
project/upstream-audiocodec/AudioCodec.vcxproj
project/upstream-audiocodec/AudioCodec.vcxproj.Filters
project/upstream-audiocodec/AudioCodec.inf
project/import-manifest.json
project/import-report.txt

